@startuml system-context
title WorkflowDev — Contexto do Sistema (Issue-only, CLI + Web local)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
left to right direction

actor "Humano\n(planeja / valida)" as Human
actor "IA / Harness\n(claude-code, cursor,\ncodex, pi)" as AI

package "WorkflowDev (local)" {
  [CLI  `issues`] as CLI
  [Web local\n(127.0.0.1)] as Web
  [Núcleo\n(domain + app)] as Core
  database "Filesystem\n~/issues-manager" as FS
  [Engine PlantUML\n(@plantuml/mcp-js)] as PUML
}

Human --> CLI : cria/decide/reset\nvalida entregas
Human --> Web : board + decisão\nvisual (HITL)
AI --> CLI : claim (`next`) e\nconclui via fila

CLI --> Core
Web --> Core
Core --> FS : Issues em pastas\npor status
Core --> PUML : valida/renderiza\ndiagramas de Design
Web ..> PUML : SVG dos diagramas\n(rota .svg)

note bottom of Core
  Modelo Issue-only: cada Issue tem type (o problema)
  e action (a entrega). Trabalho maior vira novas
  Issues relacionadas (linhagem), não Tickets.
end note
@enduml
